---
---
<section class="deploy" id="deployment">
  <div class="deploy__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container deploy__inner">
    <div class="deploy__text reveal">
      <p class="overline">Operation Iraqi Freedom · 2005</p>
      <hr class="fire-rule" />
      <h2 class="display deploy__heading">
        When it counted<br/>most, I was<br/><em>the one.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="deploy__body reveal">
      <p>
        When my unit deployed to Iraq, I deployed as the only dual-qualified
        Mission Crew Commander on the EC-130H Compass Call airframe.
        That wasn't a title — it was a weight.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every sortie we flew depended on my expertise and my decisions.
        There was no one else. I owned it.
      </p>
      <p>
        On the ground, my squadron commander tapped me as <strong>Chief of Security</strong> —
        responsible for information security, operational security, and personnel security
        for the entire unit. I managed top secret clearance upgrades and led five airmen
        to the same standard I held in the air.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="deploy__quote">
        <p>"Always delivered better than expected. Led from the front.
        Gave her time to others freely."</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.deploy {
  position: relative;
  padding-block: var(--section-pad);
  background: var(--coal);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.deploy__bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 90% 50%, rgba(139,26,26,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.deploy__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr;
  gap: 4rem 5rem;
  align-items: start;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .deploy__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
}
.deploy__heading {
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5.5vw, 4rem);
  color: var(--white);
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.deploy__heading em {
  color: var(--amber);
  font-style: italic;
}
.deploy__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.4rem;
  color: var(--bone);
  opacity: 0.85;
}
.deploy__body strong {
  color: var(--amber);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.deploy__quote {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--crimson);
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.deploy__quote p {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--slate);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
</style>
